âœ… Code ngáº¯n gá»n hÆ¡n - Arrow functions, destructuring, spread
âœ… Code rÃµ rÃ ng hÆ¡n - Template literals, default parameters
âœ… Code an toÃ n hÆ¡n - let/const, proper scope
